                  role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Huizi Zhang <H.Zhang-144@sms.ed.ac.uk>
Description: This package implements a model-based clustering approach 
    through hierarchical Bayesian mixtures for high-throughput mapping of 
    axon projections. The model allows for identifying groups of neurons 
    with unique projection patterns across different brain regions, 
    and investigates differences across experiments.
